title: Aphrodite Cafe and Pie Shop
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic cafe and pie shop, previously both occupying this space but in Jan 2015 the moved just across the street. The pie shop remains here. Offers a few vegan choices including tofu scramble. Ask for the vegan pie.
